title: Driver Who Witnessed Walcha Derby Crash Speaks | 10 News+
description: Yesterday, a freak accident at a demolition derby in Walcha, in north-west New South Wales, left 13 people injured. 10 News+ spoke to Todd Cleal, a driver who witnessed the crash, and Blake Taylor, the brother of the driver involved in the incident. Taylor described the scene as looking "like a bomb went off,” and Cleal has asked anyone involved to reach out for support from the tight-knit Derby community.
